Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.01,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,40)}第180話 紅色殺意的夜想曲(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.93,0:00:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.73,0:00:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国来的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴调音 暗藏杀意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.14,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.69,0:01:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色杀意的夜想曲(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.54,0:01:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加那娱乐集团可是个大公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长先生有什么事情么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.84,0:02:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的公司要出版杰拉尔天马的CD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.45,0:02:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备开一个签约和庆祝的晚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马终于到日本来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国流行乐坛现在最红的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的日本歌手 我当然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于他过去的经历谁也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从晚会的日期定下之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.74,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子美咲的周围就怪事不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多次电话没人讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有写发送人的玫瑰花束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐吓信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视我的爱的人会下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一封是昨天寄来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇的宴会马上就要开幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受恐怖的晚会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚会是三天以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.94,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也不能取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我很为妻子担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有什么怀疑对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的签约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是秘密进行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚会的知情者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们夫妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那四个准备出席晚会的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抛弃了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我至今无法忘记你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远关注着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴的发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天马的红色爱的夜想曲的日文歌词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天给你献上一朵花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.15,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金盏花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.25,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半边莲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大红的大理花以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情的曲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.33,0:04:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这歌词哪里好  兰这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能够见到天马 太幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可是去干活的 干活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.24,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是会长的朋友毛利田一家 记住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.35,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能让人知道我是个名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.85,0:04:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 看不出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.65,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都注意点举止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我该说的话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 从入口到门前还要开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像外国电影一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真豪华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大富豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有点像恐怖电影里面的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓人打雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还是晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想见杰拉尔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕和这没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛利田先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我就是受到邀请的毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.03,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.03,0:05:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正等你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的秘书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫德大寺昌代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是会场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术品都很出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我妻子的收藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请这边坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能先参观一下你的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德大寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他们去参观一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.23,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你们去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任集团公司加那音乐出版社社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌代去厨房帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人好像讨厌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是大厅的正上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息室的最里面是钢琴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是大富豪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室内还有回廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会碰坏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是装饰品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.14,0:08:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,材料和制作方法都和真的没有区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是真的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴室的隔壁是我的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间也很有品位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们夫妇的结婚照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在斐济
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大学时代就是同一个音乐小组的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往了一年就结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无比羡慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情经常发生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一个沙哑的男人声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻声低语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我接 他立刻就挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么怀疑对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有和信一起寄来的这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你不知情的时候拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天早上和金盏花一起放在门廊上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是昨天照的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是觉得有人在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰的下一个是金盏花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被人注视着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以毛利小五郎的名誉保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力保护美咲女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人们到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是杰拉尔天马的经纪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是米歇尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我哥哥加那善则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的妻子美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.96,0:10:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 他还有事 迟到三十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 那边那位是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的旧友毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的小孩兰和柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田 这是我弟弟秀树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任加那音乐出版社的副社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请这边坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着就好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来干什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带外人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔的契约 现在可是关键时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你任性的去了法国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张的把杰拉尔带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了公司才这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你批评我毫无道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.64,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么做 你在美咲面前就不能露脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.95,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想方设法要和美咲亲近吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.56,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你和德大寺又是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个公司都传遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻话 我和她之间没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.73,0:11:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 我一定要签了约给你看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.65,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔差不多该到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去门廊等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一趟卫生间再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下一道菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田的酒也喝完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失陪一下 去补妆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲没人陪着没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 干活 干活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女化妆室我怎么进得去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 你去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.83,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被雷击了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不对头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.25,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门锁着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪里去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.25,0:13:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.95,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是谁关了电闸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.19,0:13:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是谁突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半边莲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果然还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐 那首歌里也有这个花名的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.05,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色爱的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红玫瑰 金盏花和半边莲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是犯人至今送来的花吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远关注着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴的发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.73,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么按照杰拉尔天马的歌词在骚扰美咲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骚扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.34,0:14:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么人故意在骚扰美丽的夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 非常抱歉 晚会开到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我问几个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把电闸拉起来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我赶过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把楼梯旁边的电闸拉起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀树当时在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利田 你是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我不是毛利田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是侦探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个有名的..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.70,0:15:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你锁上的门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我正要补妆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯突然灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人从后面袭击我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有看见犯人的脸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的不是十分清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披着披风 面无表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外国人的容貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.53,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 为什么看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.83,0:15:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了迎接杰拉尔 我去了门廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀树在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听到救命的喊声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人就到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔是我们重要的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.89,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是今天的主角 杰拉尔天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一楼没有人 所以我就上来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚出了一点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们下楼谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门上了锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时犯人已经在房间里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提前离开大厅的所有人都有作案时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电闸是谁拉断的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人不止一个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.54,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断口还是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些小块的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是神秘东西留下的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案发当时 各位都在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在洗手间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一停电我就着急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.89,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在厨房看着夫人烤的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多都淋湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大门那里下的计程车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.56,0:17:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子又不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.83,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能去我的房间给我把药拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的照片拍的就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发生过激烈的打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲和杰拉尔天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是美咲结婚之前半年吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又要说你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 不行 兰 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.85,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前和美咲有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 太没礼貌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀树 你事先就知道 故意的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.94,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你结婚之前我确实和这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原名叫天马纯也得人恋爱过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他是个默默无闻的音乐家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是十年前的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.15,0:19:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了杰拉尔天马的资料大吃一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上怎么有这么巧的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.03,0:19:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 这是给你带的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家里手工制作的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本是买不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就请允许我先尝尝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们喝果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位请过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然还是有戒备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我还烤着蛋糕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌代 你去地下室把那套银茶具拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位尝尝我特制的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.40,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为让你的公司出版夜想曲的条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想稍加改动 重新制作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新制作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔本人强烈要求这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花是在门廊找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.16,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大理花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花语是背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 能不能给我们唱几首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易请到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你袭击美咲的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你还有谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃跑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡搅蛮缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.85,0:22:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色爱的夜想曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.46,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌是十年前天马送给美咲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.23,0:24:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是血么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是袭击美咲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.34,0:24:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.64,0:24:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色杀意的夜想曲(后篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.95,0:24:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.75,0:24:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集揭开谜底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.65,0:24:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘀嘀嘀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.75,0:24:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.86,0:24:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结案的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.96,0:24:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.96,0:00:24.83,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}正因你我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}喜好各异 脚程与表达方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.60,0:00:40.77,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}如今的我们 在对方的记忆中 正渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.56,0:00:48.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我摸索过 却开始寻找 其他人 的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.35,0:00:55.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我比想象中活得更坚强 去追求 特别的 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.53,0:00:59.37,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}苦恼着　难以应付的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.66,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.79,0:01:10.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}为了不会再度迷失 那只手 我绝不松开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.43,0:01:13.05,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}即使是彼此受伤的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.18,0:01:24.56,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}我只是 一直在这个 迷惘的时空中 搜寻着答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.81,0:01:31.03,Opening,NTP,0000,0316,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}{\fad(0,1000)}到下个地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.81,0:01:31.03,Opening,NTP,0000,-0111,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}{\fad(0,1000)}you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.61,0:01:35.40,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-3}{\fad(0,1000)}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.53,0:01:42.58,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\shad1.5\fsp-1.4}{\fad(0,1000)}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.03,0:00:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.96,0:22:40.21,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}不知道　该用什么话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.63,0:22:47.30,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}才能　告诉你我真正的感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.39,0:22:56.60,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}从那时起　不知过了多少季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.27,0:23:02.52,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}虽然时间无情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.32,0:23:10.07,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}你却总是　微笑地陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.99,0:23:20.34,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}我没对你说出口的 至今 还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.30,Ending,NTP,0000,0225,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}Secret of my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.30,Ending,NTP,0000,-0230,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}请你不要怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.42,0:23:31.43,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}无论何时　只要还有少许未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:36.43,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}真相　是紧握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,0448,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}{\fscx130}I can't say
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,0180,0000,,{\be1\fsp-3}请给我点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.56,0:23:43.11,Ending,NTP,0000,-0231,0000,,{\be1\fsp-1.8}{\fscx130}I'm waiting for a chance
